title: 'Back to the Moon': Time magazine salutes Artemis 2 astronauts in special commemorative cover issue
description: While the world awaits the first crewed moon mission in more than 50 years, Time magazine is celebrating the momentous event with a special Artemis 2 cover issue that hit newsstands on Jan. 30.
